      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled right off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is truly pristine inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014come see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
