    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46), an uncompromising example of the marque\u2019s engineering prowess. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a high-revving, linear power band. This specimen is in museum-grade condition; the chassis is structurally flawless with no subframe fatigue, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile shifts. The suspension remains taut, preserving the celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. Every panel retains its factory-applied finish with no imperfections, and the interior's Nappa leather remains supple and free of wear. This is a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
