      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained under climate-controlled garage storage and exclusively hand-washed to preserve the mirror-like finish of the original paint, which is free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in pristine condition, featuring supple, unscuffed leather and that distinct new-car scent, completely free from any smoke or pet history. Mechanically, the car is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, documented paper trail included. With ultra-low mileage and zero signs of wear on the touchpoints, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection in every detail.",
